org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.resourcemanager.scheduler.policy

Interface SchedulableEntity

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FiCaSchedulerApp, FifoAppAttempt, FSAppAttempt, SchedulerApplicationAttempt

    public interface SchedulableEntity
    A SchedulableEntity is a process to be scheduled. for example, an application / application attempt
